====哺乳动物====

再生的机制在[[墨菲罗斯大鼠|墨菲罗斯大鼠]]中被发现，并且与p21基因的失活有关<ref name="Heber-Katz_2010">{{cite journal | author = Bedelbaeva K, Snyder A, Gourevitch D, Clark L, Zhang X-M, Leferovich J, Cheverud JM, Lieberman P, Heber-Katz E | title = Lack of p21 expression links cell cycle control and appendage regeneration in mice | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences | volume = 107 | issue = 11 | pages = 5845–50 | pmid = 20231440 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.1000830107 | url = http://www.pnas.org/content/early/2010/03/08/1000830107.abstract | laysummary = http://www.physorg.com/news187879295.html | laysource = PhysOrg.com | pmc = 2851923 | date = March 2010 | access-date = 2013-12-08 | archive-date = 2019-04-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190413214125/https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2010/03/08/1000830107.abstract | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.popsci.com/science/article/2010-03/humans-could-regenerate-tissue-newts-switchin-single-gene |title=Humans Could Regenerate Tissue Like Newts By Switching Off a Single Gene |accessdate=2013-12-08 |archive-date=2017-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918005046/http://www.popsci.com/science/article/2010-03/humans-could-regenerate-tissue-newts-switchin-single-gene |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

至少两种[[非洲刺毛鼠屬|刺毛鼠屬]]，分别是''Acomys kempi''与''Acomys percivali''，能够完全再生由[[自割|自割]]受损的组织。这些物种可再生毛囊、皮肤、[[汗腺|汗腺]]、毛皮和软骨。<ref>{{cite web
| coauthors = Ashley W. Seifert, Stephen G. Kiama etal
